            <h3>What is Matched Betting?</h3>
            <p>Matched betting is a strategy to profit from free bets and promotions offered by bookmakers. By placing a back bet (betting for something to happen) with a bookmaker and a lay bet (betting against it happening) on a betting exchange, you can cover all outcomes and guarantee a profit.</p>
            
            <h3>How to Use This Tracker</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Add Your Bets:</strong> Use the form on the Dashboard tab to record each matched bet</li>
                <li><strong>Calculate Stakes:</strong> Use the Calculator tab to determine the correct lay stake</li>
                <li><strong>Track Progress:</strong> Monitor your profits on the Dashboard</li>
                <li><strong>Review History:</strong> View all your past bets in the My Bets tab</li>
            </ol>
            
            <h3>Technical Details</h3>
            <p>This application uses:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>HTML5, CSS3, and vanilla JavaScript</li>
                <li>Local Storage for data persistence</li>
                <li>Responsive design for mobile compatibility</li>
                <li>Font Awesome icons for UI elements</li>
            </ul>
            
